<STRONG><H1><I>Ants are everywhere!</I></H1></STRONG>
What do I have to do to keep them from moving into my home?
and what about getting them out of my garden? my roses?
I want to do it without using chemicals that can harm me and my
environment!
These questions and more will be answered in these pages of  <IMG SRC = goldstar.gif ></A> Dances with Ants.
I have been doing Natural Pest Control since 1972 and I have developed a very simple yet
safe way of controlling your ants.
