send you our Digital Newsletter once. This Digital newsletter is the same one
 we send to our IGA members, this keeps them informed as to wahts going on
in IGA (Invisible Gardeners of America) and to keep them updated on our website
site The Organic InfoBank. This Digital Newsletter will help to introduce you to our club.

