<head>
<title>CNR-IAN Istituto Automazione Navale, Genoa, Italy</title>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 2.0">
