<h1 align="center">Robotics Department</h1>

<h4 align="center">Head: <a href="/staff/cv_gian.htm">Gianmarco
Veruggio</a></h4>

<p>The Robotics Department at <a href="/Welcome.html">CNR-IAN</a>
was set up in 1989 to advance understanding in marine robotics,
particularly concerning Unmanned Underwater Vehicles (UUVs) and
tele-operated systems. </p>

<p align="left"><font size="5"><strong><i>Areas of investigation</i></strong></font><font
size="4">: </font></p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> <a href="intcontr.htm">Intelligent
Control</a></p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> <a href="navcntrl.htm">Navigation Control</a> </p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> Acoustic <a href="acousnav.htm">Localization
&amp; World Modeling</a> </p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> Underwater <a href="manip.htm">Manipulation</a> </p>

<p align="left">&nbsp;<font color="#400040" size="5"><strong><i>Major
projects, activities and developments:</i></strong></font><font
size="4"> </font></p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> <a href="amadeus.htm">AMADEUS</a> Project
(Advanced Manipulation for Deep Underwater Systems) </p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> <a href="sara.htm">SARA</a> Project
(Sottomarino Autonomo Robotizzato Antartico) </p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> <a href="scienapp.htm">Scientific
missions</a> (including <a href="scienapp.htm#ANTARCTICA">Antarctic
Expeditions</a>) </p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> Construction and <a href="test.htm">testing</a>
of <a href="vehicle.htm">prototype</a><a href="vehicle.htm"> UUVs</a></p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> <a href="simul.htm">Simulation</a> </p>

<p align="left"><img
src="file:///E:/frontpage/clipart/Punti elenco/Spirale blu.gif"
width="15" height="13"> Data Base of <a
href="archit/dbarchit.htm">Control Architectures</a> </p>

<p align="left">&nbsp;</p>

<hr>

<p align="center">&nbsp;<strong><i><img src="/icons/bluebull.gif"
align="center" width="14" height="14"> </i></strong><a
href="lab.htm"><strong><i>Laboratories</i></strong></a><strong><i> <img
src="/icons/bluebull.gif" align="center" width="14" height="14"> </i></strong><a
href="/staff/teamrob.htm"><strong><i>Team</i></strong></a><strong><i> <img
src="/icons/bluebull.gif" align="center" width="14" height="14"> </i></strong><a
href="/backgrnd.htm#marine"><strong><i>Background</i></strong></a><strong><i> <img
src="/icons/bluebull.gif" align="center" width="14" height="14"> </i></strong><br>
<img src="/icons/world.gif" alt="[world]" align="center"
vspace="10" width="40" height="40"> <a
href="/robotics/wwwsites.htm"><strong>Related WWW sites</strong></a> </p>

<p align="left">Further information on the Robotics Department
can be obtained from <a href="mailto:gian@ian.ge.cnr.it">gian@ian.ge.cnr.it</a><br>
</p>

