<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT03-B18-21</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA085-000610-B038-123</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://srvnt2.ian.ge.cnr.it:80/geninfo.htm 150.145.4.16 19970216120148 text/html 3382
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
