<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT03-B18-22</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA085-000610-B038-168</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://srvnt2.ian.ge.cnr.it:80/backgrnd.htm 150.145.4.16 19970216120209 text/html 17278
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/3.0
Date: Sun, 16 Feb 1997 12:02:53 GMT
