<p>&#160;</p>
<table>
<tr><td width=33%><img src="pictures/gabry.jpg" align=bottom width=157 height=207></td><td width=33%><strong>Gabriele Bruzzone</strong><br>
Research Scientist<p>Phone: + 39 10 6475657<br>
