thousands of such well-worn statements about the coming world government.
We have selected some of the very best and well known.</P>

<P>INVESTIGATOR'S NOTE: As the investigator will notice not all of the
quotes are documented as to date and place of utterance. This will trouble
some. If this is a problem to the reader, he should either eliminate those
quotes, or consider, as police investigators do, the great preponderance
of evidence pointing toward any given hypothesis! In addition, as in other
investigations, sometimes the investigator must look at the results to
accurately check the validity of the information one is receiving. This
is to say, that may times we must look to see if what the statement purported
would occur, ACTUALLY OCCURRED, in order to check and see if the original
information received was valid. As the investigator will recognize, this
is the same process used by law enforcement in proving the reliability
of a Confidential Informant (CI). The reader will readily see that what
the undocumented statements listed in this publication exposed, or stated
would occur in the future, has either occurred, or is in the process of
taking place today. Therein lies the proof of the validity of the original
statements and why they were chosen to be included in this publication.</P>

