our 2nd President, John Adams:</P>

<P>&quot;YOUR HAVE RIGHTS ANTECEDENT TO ALL EARTHLY GOVERNMENTS; RIGHTS
THAT CANNOT BE REPEALED OR RESTRAINED BY HUMAN LAWS; RIGHTS DERIVED FROM
THE GREAT LEGISLATOR OF THE UNIVERSE.&quot;</P>

