<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>RWT: Magazine Articles</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><H1 ALIGN="CENTER"><IMG
ALIGN="MIDDLE" SRC="bluer.gif" HSPACE="10">Magazine Articles<IMG
ALIGN="MIDDLE" SRC="bluel.gif" HSPACE="10"></H1>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">Below are magazine articles about Workspace or RWT. Look for
another <BR>upcoming article in <I>Industrial Robot</I> .</P>
<CENTER><TABLE ALIGN="CENTER"><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><A
