Myers, FL</A> is looking for talented individuals<BR> to represent and support
Workspace&#174;, the first and only true,<BR> PC-based Robot Simulation and off
line programming software.<BR> Our company has growth and substantial earnings
potential for <BR>the right individuals. We have opportunities in the following
areas:</B></P>
