<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="VISU/Cover2.jpg" HEIGHT=196 WIDTH=346><BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<TT>CONCAWE is the oil companies'<BR>
<BR>
European organization for<BR>
<BR>
environment, health and safety. <BR>
<BR>
The emphasis of its work lies on<BR>
<BR>
technical and economic studies<BR>
<BR>
relevant to oil refining, distribution<BR>
<BR>
and marketing in Europe.<BR>
<BR>
CONCAWE was established in 1963<BR>
<BR>
in The Hague, and in 1990 its<BR>
<BR>
Secretariat was moved to Brussels.</TT> </TD>
</TR>
