<h1>C o n t e n t s</CENTER>
</H1><br><br>
<P><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"0" ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="More.htm">More about CONCAWE</A></B><BR>
CONCAWE is an effective and principled forum which exists because its <BR>
rational approach is essential to the proper resolution of complex issues.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Current.htm">Current activities</A></B><BR>
CONCAWE continues to define reliable technical and economic data on <BR>
oil-related environment, health and safety topics.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Euair.htm">EU Air Quality Framework Directive development</A></B><BR>
CONCAWE is helping with Industry's contribution to the process.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Air.htm">Air quality standards-a focus on ozone</A></B><BR>
Relationships between ozone exposure levels, human health effects and annual
crops growth.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Costing.htm">Costing of fuels for the European Auto/Oil Programme</A></B><BR>
Extreme constraints on road transport fuels compositions can be very costly
<BR>
and the resulting incremental emissions reductions are limited.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Vehicle.htm">Vehicle emissions and fuel specifications update</A></B><BR>
Key points from the 1995 update on motor vehicle emission regulations and
fuel specifications.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Alternat.htm">Alternative fuels for road transport</A></B><BR>
Niche markets exist when special advantages outweigh drawbacks, but <BR>
biofuels struggle when crude oil remains cheap and plentiful.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Automot.htm">CONCAWE's Automotive Emissions Management Group</A></B><BR>
The current work and future challenges.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<B><A HREF="Update.htm">Dossier update: gas oils</A></B><BR>
The latest CONCAWE product dossier provides health, safety and <BR>
environmental data on diesel fuels and heating oils.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Accident.htm">European oil industry accident statistics</A></B><BR>
CONCAWE has started to collect information on the frequency of accidents
in <BR>
its Member Companies which demonstrate a good and improving safety performance.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
ALIGN=bottom><BR>
<BR>
<B><A HREF="Pipeline.htm">CONCAWE's oil pipelines database enlargement</A></B><BR>
The oil pipelines inventory monitored by CONCAWE has expanded to incorporate
<BR>
non-commercially owned pipelines and a step out eastwards is being investigated.<BR>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="../../VISU/VOLUME5/Bol2.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="16" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0" 
