<DOCNO>WT03-B18-157</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA019-000199-B017-104</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www62.interpac.be:80/HTML/VOLUME5/Costing.htm 193.53.125.113 19970106200812 text/html 7036
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0.interpac
