<DOCNO>WT03-B18-158</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA019-000199-B017-114</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www62.interpac.be:80/HTML/VOLUME5/Vehicle.htm 193.53.125.113 19970106200821 text/html 7887
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
