Coast Express Rail  Schedule Effective <B>November 11, 1996</B>: <P>
<P>

<ul>
<li><a href = "/www/railroads/coaster.html#Map">Route Map</a></li>
<li><a href = "/www/railroads/coaster_info.html">General Info</a></li>
