<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Southern California Railroad Resources
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<center>
<H1>Southern California Railroad Resources</H1>
<P>

Welcome to the Text Only Division of the Southern California Railroad
Resources.<P>

You are operating under authority number
<img src="/htbin/access_odometer/www/railroads/railindex.html"><p>

<a href="/www/railroads/railroads.html">
Go to the Graphical Version</a><P>

</center>

<HR>

